#: includes/Admin.php:376
msgid ""
"The B2Brouter plugin allows you to automatically generate and send "
"electronic invoices for your WooCommerce orders."
msgstr ""
"Das B2Brouter-Plugin ermöglicht es Ihnen, automatisch elektronische "
"Rechnungen für Ihre WooCommerce-Bestellungen zu erstellen und zu versenden."

#: includes/Admin.php:386
msgid "Next Steps"
msgstr "Nächste Schritte"

#: includes/Admin.php:387
msgid "Step 1 — Get your B2Brouter credentials"
msgstr "Schritt 1 — B2Brouter-Zugangsdaten erhalten"

#: includes/Admin.php:389
msgid "Register at app.b2brouter.net"
msgstr "Bei app.b2brouter.net registrieren"

#: includes/Admin.php:390
msgid "Purchase an eDocExchange subscription."
msgstr "Erwerben Sie ein eDocExchange-Abonnement."

#: includes/Admin.php:390
msgid "First month is for free!"
msgstr "Der erste Monat ist kostenlos!"

#: includes/Admin.php:391
msgid "Go to Developers → API Keys in your B2Brouter dashboard."
msgstr "Gehen Sie zu Entwickler → API-Schlüssel in Ihrem B2Brouter-Dashboard."

#: includes/Admin.php:392
msgid "Copy the API key and store it safely."
msgstr "Kopieren Sie den API-Schlüssel und bewahren Sie ihn sicher auf."

#: includes/Admin.php:394
msgid "Step 2 — Configure the plugin"
msgstr "Schritt 2 — Plugin konfigurieren"

#: includes/Admin.php:396
msgid "In WordPress, go to Invoices → Settings."
msgstr "Gehen Sie in WordPress zu Rechnungen → Einstellungen."

#: includes/Admin.php:397
msgid "Paste your B2Brouter API key."
msgstr "Fügen Sie Ihren B2Brouter-API-Schlüssel ein."

#: includes/Admin.php:398
msgid ""
"Click Validate Key. If the key is correct, the plugin will display your "
"account information."
msgstr ""
"Klicken Sie auf Schlüssel überprüfen. Wenn der Schlüssel korrekt ist, zeigt "
"das Plugin Ihre Kontoinformationen an."

#: includes/Admin.php:402
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Voraussetzungen"

#: includes/Admin.php:404
msgid "A B2Brouter account with an active eDocExchange subscription"
msgstr "Ein B2Brouter-Konto mit einem aktiven eDocExchange-Abonnement"

#: includes/Admin.php:405
msgid "WordPress 5.8 or higher"
msgstr "WordPress 5.8 oder höher"

#: includes/Admin.php:406
msgid "WooCommerce 5.0 or higher, installed and active"
msgstr "WooCommerce 5.0 oder höher, installiert und aktiv"

#: includes/Admin.php:407
msgid "PHP 7.4 or higher"
msgstr "PHP 7.4 oder höher"

#: includes/Admin.php:414
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "So funktioniert es"

#: includes/Admin.php:416
msgid ""
"Advanced configuration (transports, formats, taxes) is done in your "
"B2Brouter account."
msgstr ""
"Die erweiterte Konfiguration (Transporte, Formate, Steuern) erfolgt in Ihrem "
"B2Brouter-Konto."

#: includes/Admin.php:417
msgid ""
"When an order is completed, the plugin automatically generates the invoice "
"via the B2Brouter API."
msgstr ""
"Wenn eine Bestellung abgeschlossen wird, erstellt das Plugin automatisch die "
"Rechnung über die B2Brouter-API."

#: includes/Admin.php:418
msgid ""
"B2Brouter sends the invoice to your customer using your configured transport "
"(email, Peppol, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"B2Brouter sendet die Rechnung an Ihren Kunden über den konfigurierten "
"Transport (E-Mail, Peppol, etc.)."

#: includes/Admin.php:419
msgid ""
"Your customers can also download their invoices from their account page."
msgstr ""
"Ihre Kunden können ihre Rechnungen auch von ihrer Kontoseite herunterladen."

#: includes/Admin.php:420
msgid "Credit notes are generated automatically when you process a refund."
msgstr ""
"Gutschriften werden automatisch erstellt, wenn Sie eine Rückerstattung "
"verarbeiten."

#: includes/Admin.php:422
msgid "Ready to get started?"
msgstr "Bereit loszulegen?"

#: includes/Admin.php:425
msgid "Go to B2Brouter - Activate Subscription"
msgstr "Zu B2Brouter gehen - Abonnement aktivieren"

#: includes/Admin.php:428
msgid "Configure Plugin"
msgstr "Plugin konfigurieren"

#: includes/Admin.php:433
msgid "Benefits"
msgstr "Vorteile"

#: includes/Admin.php:435
msgid "Legal Compliance"
msgstr "Rechtskonformität"

#: includes/Admin.php:435
msgid ""
"Automatic compliance with electronic invoicing regulations across multiple "
"countries."
msgstr ""
"Automatische Einhaltung der Vorschriften zur elektronischen "
"Rechnungsstellung in mehreren Ländern."

#: includes/Admin.php:436
msgid "Time Saving"
msgstr "Zeitersparnis"

#: includes/Admin.php:436
msgid ""
"Automatic generation of electronic invoices without manual intervention."
msgstr ""
"Automatische Erstellung elektronischer Rechnungen ohne manuellen Eingriff."

#: includes/Admin.php:437
msgid "Professionalism"
msgstr "Professionalität"

#: includes/Admin.php:437
msgid "Invoices in standard formats: UBL, CII, XML, etc."
msgstr "Rechnungen in Standardformaten: UBL, CII, XML, etc."

#: includes/Admin.php:438
msgid "Cross-border"
msgstr "Grenzüberschreitend"

#: includes/Admin.php:438
msgid "Support for international B2B and B2C transactions."
msgstr "Unterstützung für internationale B2B- und B2C-Transaktionen."

#: includes/Admin.php:439
msgid "Full Integration"
msgstr "Vollständige Integration"

#: includes/Admin.php:439
msgid "Works seamlessly with WooCommerce without affecting your workflow."
msgstr ""
"Funktioniert nahtlos mit WooCommerce, ohne Ihren Arbeitsablauf zu "
"beeinträchtigen."

#: includes/Admin.php:447
msgid "Need Help?"
msgstr "Brauchen Sie Hilfe?"

#: includes/Admin.php:448
msgid ""
"Visit our GitHub repository for detailed documentation. If you need help, "
"please open an issue."
msgstr ""
"Besuchen Sie unser GitHub-Repository für die ausführliche Dokumentation. "
"Wenn Sie Hilfe benötigen, eröffnen Sie bitte ein Issue."

#: includes/Admin.php:450
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentation"

#: includes/Admin.php:451
msgid "Changelog"
msgstr "Änderungsprotokoll"

#: includes/Admin.php:452
msgid "Support"
msgstr "Support"

#: includes/Admin.php:516
msgid "Webhook secret is required when webhooks are enabled."
msgstr "Das Webhook-Geheimnis ist erforderlich, wenn Webhooks aktiviert sind."

#: includes/Admin.php:589
msgid "Settings saved successfully."
msgstr "Einstellungen erfolgreich gespeichert."

#: includes/Admin.php:594
msgid "Invoice Settings"
msgstr "Rechnungseinstellungen"

#: includes/Admin.php:599
msgid "API key is not configured. Please enter your B2Brouter API key below."
msgstr ""
"Der API-Schlüssel ist nicht konfiguriert. Bitte geben Sie unten Ihren "
"B2Brouter-API-Schlüssel ein."

#: includes/Admin.php:600 includes/Admin.php:646
msgid "Get your API key"
msgstr "API-Schlüssel erhalten"

#: includes/Admin.php:611
msgid "API Key"
msgstr "API-Schlüssel"

#: includes/Admin.php:619
msgid "Enter your B2Brouter API key"
msgstr "Geben Sie Ihren B2Brouter-API-Schlüssel ein"

#: includes/Admin.php:627
msgid "Use this account"
msgstr "Dieses Konto verwenden"

#: includes/Admin.php:639
msgid "Unknown"
msgstr "Unbekannt"

#: includes/Admin.php:645
msgid "Enter your B2Brouter API key to enable invoice generation."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie Ihren B2Brouter-API-Schlüssel ein, um die Rechnungserstellung zu "
"aktivieren."

#: includes/Admin.php:653
msgid "Environment"
msgstr "Umgebung"

#: includes/Admin.php:662
msgid "Staging"
msgstr "Staging"

#: includes/Admin.php:665
msgid "Use staging environment for testing"
msgstr "Staging-Umgebung zum Testen verwenden"

#: includes/Admin.php:672
msgid "Production"
msgstr "Produktion"

#: includes/Admin.php:675
msgid "Use production environment for live invoices"
msgstr "Produktionsumgebung für echte Rechnungen verwenden"

#: includes/Admin.php:682
msgid "Invoice Generation Mode"
msgstr "Rechnungserstellungsmodus"

#: includes/Admin.php:691
msgid "Automatic"
msgstr "Automatisch"

#: includes/Admin.php:693
msgid "Generate invoice automatically when order is completed"
msgstr "Rechnung automatisch erstellen, wenn die Bestellung abgeschlossen ist"

#: includes/Admin.php:700
msgid "Manual"
msgstr "Manuell"

#: includes/Admin.php:702
msgid "Generate invoice manually using a button in the order admin"
msgstr ""
"Rechnung manuell über eine Schaltfläche in der Bestellverwaltung erstellen"

#: includes/Admin.php:708
msgid "Webhook Configuration"
msgstr "Webhook-Konfiguration"

#: includes/Admin.php:713
msgid "Enable Webhooks"
msgstr "Webhooks aktivieren"

#: includes/Admin.php:723
msgid "Receive real-time invoice status updates from B2Brouter (recommended)."
msgstr ""
"Echtzeit-Statusaktualisierungen für Rechnungen von B2Brouter erhalten "
"(empfohlen)."

#: includes/Admin.php:731
msgid "Webhook URL"
msgstr "Webhook-URL"

#: includes/Admin.php:744
msgid "Copied!"
msgstr "Kopiert!"

#: includes/Admin.php:744 includes/Admin.php:745
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopieren"

#: includes/Admin.php:748
msgid "Enter this URL in your B2Brouter dashboard webhook settings."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie diese URL in den Webhook-Einstellungen Ihres B2Brouter-Dashboards "
"ein."

#: includes/Admin.php:756
msgid "Webhook Secret"
msgstr "Webhook-Geheimnis"

#: includes/Admin.php:766
msgid ""
"Enter the webhook secret from your B2Brouter dashboard to verify webhook "
"authenticity."
msgstr ""
"Geben Sie das Webhook-Geheimnis aus Ihrem B2Brouter-Dashboard ein, um die "
"Webhook-Authentizität zu überprüfen."

#: includes/Admin.php:774
msgid "Fallback Polling"
msgstr "Fallback-Abfrage"

#: includes/Admin.php:784
msgid ""
"Keep polling as backup (checks every 6 hours if webhook fails). Recommended "
"for reliability."
msgstr ""
"Abfrage als Backup beibehalten (prüft alle 6 Stunden, wenn der Webhook "
"fehlschlägt). Empfohlen für Zuverlässigkeit."

#: includes/Admin.php:790
msgid "Invoice Numbering & Series"
msgstr "Rechnungsnummerierung & Serien"

#: includes/Admin.php:794
msgid "Invoice Series Code"
msgstr "Rechnungsseriencode"

#: includes/Admin.php:802
msgid "e.g., INV, S01"
msgstr "z. B. INV, S01"

#: includes/Admin.php:804
msgid ""
"Define one invoice series code for all invoices. B2Brouter allows one series "
"per invoice type. Leave empty to use B2Brouter default."
msgstr ""
"Definieren Sie einen Seriencode für alle Rechnungen. B2Brouter erlaubt eine "
"Serie pro Rechnungstyp. Leer lassen, um den B2Brouter-Standard zu verwenden."

#: includes/Admin.php:811
msgid "Credit Note Series Code"
msgstr "Gutschrift-Seriencode"

#: includes/Admin.php:819
msgid "e.g., CN, R01"
msgstr "z. B. GS, R01"

#: includes/Admin.php:821
msgid ""
"Define one credit note series code for all credit notes. B2Brouter allows "
"one series per type. Leave empty to use the same series as invoices."
msgstr ""
"Definieren Sie einen Seriencode für alle Gutschriften. B2Brouter erlaubt "
"eine Serie pro Typ. Leer lassen, um dieselbe Serie wie bei Rechnungen zu "
"verwenden."

#: includes/Admin.php:828
msgid "Invoice Numbering Pattern"
msgstr "Rechnungsnummerierungsmuster"

#: includes/Admin.php:837
msgid "Automatic (B2Brouter manages numbering)"
msgstr "Automatisch (B2Brouter verwaltet die Nummerierung)"

#: includes/Admin.php:839
msgid "Let B2Brouter automatically assign invoice numbers"
msgstr "B2Brouter automatisch Rechnungsnummern zuweisen lassen"

#: includes/Admin.php:846
msgid "WooCommerce Order Number"
msgstr "WooCommerce-Bestellnummer"

#: includes/Admin.php:848
msgid "Use the WooCommerce order number as the invoice number"
msgstr "Die WooCommerce-Bestellnummer als Rechnungsnummer verwenden"

#: includes/Admin.php:855
msgid "Sequential (plugin-managed)"
msgstr "Sequenziell (plugin-verwaltet)"

#: includes/Admin.php:857
msgid "Plugin maintains sequential numbering per series (starts at 1)"
msgstr ""
"Das Plugin pflegt eine sequenzielle Nummerierung pro Serie (beginnt bei 1)"

#: includes/Admin.php:864
msgid "Custom Pattern"
msgstr "Benutzerdefiniertes Muster"

#: includes/Admin.php:874
msgid ""
"Available placeholders: {order_id}, {order_number}, {year}, {month}, {day}. "
"Note: Series code is defined separately above and will be prefixed "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Verfügbare Platzhalter: {order_id}, {order_number}, {year}, {month}, {day}. "
"Hinweis: Der Seriencode wird oben separat definiert und automatisch "
"vorangestellt."

#: includes/Admin.php:881
msgid "PDF Options"
msgstr "PDF-Optionen"

#: includes/Admin.php:885
msgid "Automatic PDF Caching"
msgstr "Automatische PDF-Zwischenspeicherung"

#: includes/Admin.php:894
msgid "Automatically download and cache PDF when invoice is generated"
msgstr ""
"PDF automatisch herunterladen und zwischenspeichern, wenn die Rechnung "
"erstellt wird"

#: includes/Admin.php:897
msgid ""
"When enabled, PDFs will be automatically downloaded from B2Brouter and "
"stored locally when an invoice is generated. This improves performance and "
"reduces API calls."
msgstr ""
"Wenn aktiviert, werden PDFs automatisch von B2Brouter heruntergeladen und "
"lokal gespeichert, wenn eine Rechnung erstellt wird. Dies verbessert die "
"Leistung und reduziert API-Aufrufe."

#: includes/Admin.php:905
msgid "PDF Storage Location"
msgstr "PDF-Speicherort"

#: includes/Admin.php:910
msgid ""
"Invoice PDFs are stored in this directory. Files are protected from direct "
"access via .htaccess rules."
msgstr ""
"Rechnungs-PDFs werden in diesem Verzeichnis gespeichert. Dateien sind "
"durch .htaccess-Regeln vor direktem Zugriff geschützt."

#: includes/Admin.php:928
#, php-format
msgid "Currently storing %d PDF(s) using %s of disk space"
msgstr "Derzeit %d PDF(s) gespeichert, %s Speicherplatz verwendet"

#: includes/Admin.php:937
msgid "Directory will be created automatically when first PDF is downloaded"
msgstr ""
"Das Verzeichnis wird automatisch erstellt, wenn das erste PDF "
"heruntergeladen wird"

#: includes/Admin.php:945
msgid "Email PDF Attachments"
msgstr "PDF-E-Mail-Anhänge"

#: includes/Admin.php:954
msgid "Attach PDF to Order Completed email (sent to customer)"
msgstr ""
"PDF an Bestellung-abgeschlossen-E-Mail anhängen (wird an den Kunden gesendet)"

#: includes/Admin.php:962
msgid "Attach PDF to Customer Invoice email"
msgstr "PDF an Kundenrechnungs-E-Mail anhängen"

#: includes/Admin.php:970
msgid "Attach PDF to Refunded Order email (credit note/rectificative)"
msgstr "PDF an Rückerstattungs-E-Mail anhängen (Gutschrift/Korrektur)"

#: includes/Admin.php:973
msgid ""
"Automatically attach invoice PDFs to customer emails. \"Order Completed\" is "
"sent when orders are fulfilled. \"Customer Invoice\" is sent for pending/"
"unpaid orders or when manually sent from admin panel. \"Refunded Order\" is "
"sent when orders are refunded."
msgstr ""
"Rechnungs-PDFs automatisch an Kunden-E-Mails anhängen. \"Bestellung "
"abgeschlossen\" wird gesendet, wenn Bestellungen ausgeführt werden. "
"\"Kundenrechnung\" wird für ausstehende/unbezahlte Bestellungen oder bei "
"manuellem Versand aus dem Admin-Panel gesendet. \"Rückerstattete "
"Bestellung\" wird gesendet, wenn Bestellungen erstattet werden."

#: includes/Admin.php:981
msgid "Automatic Cleanup"
msgstr "Automatische Bereinigung"

#: includes/Admin.php:990
msgid "Automatically delete old cached PDFs"
msgstr "Alte zwischengespeicherte PDFs automatisch löschen"

#: includes/Admin.php:994
msgid "Delete PDFs older than"
msgstr "PDFs löschen, die älter sind als"

#: includes/Admin.php:1001
msgid "days"
msgstr "Tage"

#: includes/Admin.php:1004
msgid ""
"When enabled, PDFs older than the specified number of days will be "
"automatically deleted daily via cron job. This helps manage disk space usage."
msgstr ""
"Wenn aktiviert, werden PDFs, die älter als die angegebene Anzahl von Tagen "
"sind, täglich automatisch per Cron-Job gelöscht. Dies hilft bei der "
"Verwaltung des Speicherplatzverbrauchs."

#: includes/Admin.php:1011
msgid "Plugin Information"
msgstr "Plugin-Informationen"

#: includes/Admin.php:1015
msgid "Transaction Counter"
msgstr "Transaktionszähler"

#: includes/Admin.php:1019
msgid "Total number of invoices generated from this plugin"
msgstr "Gesamtanzahl der von diesem Plugin erstellten Rechnungen"

#: includes/Admin.php:1025
msgid "B2Brouter Account"
msgstr "B2Brouter-Konto"

#: includes/Admin.php:1029
msgid "Access B2Brouter Account Settings"
msgstr "B2Brouter-Kontoeinstellungen aufrufen"

#: includes/Admin.php:1031
msgid ""
"Configure advanced settings like transports, formats, and taxes in your "
"B2Brouter account."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurieren Sie erweiterte Einstellungen wie Transporte, Formate und "
"Steuern in Ihrem B2Brouter-Konto."

#: includes/Admin.php:1038
msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "Einstellungen speichern"

#: includes/Admin.php:1054
